      <p class="nl-lede">
        Neolect connects to every source your deals live in, unifies the
        scattered signals into one trusted view of each opportunity, and gives
        your team what it needs to forecast accurately and close faster.
      </p>
      <ol class="nl-steps">
        <li>
          <span class="nl-step-n">01</span>
          <span class="nl-step-t">
            <strong>Connect your sources</strong>
            <span>Email, calls, chat, enrichment, and your data stack flow into one layer.</span>
          </span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="nl-step-n">02</span>
          <span class="nl-step-t">
            <strong>Capture at the source</strong>
            <span>Activity is logged automatically — no rep data entry, and nothing slips through.</span>
          </span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="nl-step-n">03</span>
          <span class="nl-step-t">
            <strong>Enrich and reconcile</strong>
            <span>Every signal is reconciled into a single, governed view of the deal.</span>
          </span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="nl-step-n">04</span>
          <span class="nl-step-t">
            <strong>Forecast better, close faster</strong>
            <span>Your team acts on the full picture, not stale CRM fields.</span>
          </span>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>

